OL,3,CMan dies after being struck by car on
OL,4,Cmain city route
OL,6,FA man has been killed after being hit
OL,7,Fby a car on one of Manchester's major
OL,8,Froads.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to
OL,11,FMancunian Way near the city centre at
OL,12,F12.50am on Friday to find that a man
OL,13,Fin his 20s had been struck by a
OL,14,FVolkswagen Passat while apparently
OL,15,Fcrossing the road.
OL,17,FGreater Manchester Police said the car
OL,18,Fwas merging from a slip road onto the
OL,19,Fmain carriageway when the incident
OL,20,Fhappened.
