OL,4,Cmain city route
OL,6,FThe pedestrian suffered significant
OL,7,Finjuries and died at the scene, GMP
OL,8,Fsaid.
OL,10,FPolice arrested the driver, a man in
OL,11,Fhis 40s, on suspicion of causing death
OL,12,Fby careless driving.
OL,14,FA blue forensic tent has been erected
OL,15,Fon the carriageway, while pavements
OL,16,Fclose to the road have been taped off.
OL,18,FA GMP spokesperson said: "Our Serious
OL,19,FCollision Investigation Unit are now
OL,20,Fappealing for anyone who may have
OL,21,Fwitnessed the incident to come forward.
