OL,6,F"They are keen to speak to anyone who
OL,7,Fmay have CCTV footage, dashcam or
OL,8,Fmobile phone footage from the area in
OL,9,Fthe moments leading up to the
OL,10,Fincident."
OL,12,FMancunian Way was closed in both
OL,13,Fdirections soon afterwards but has now
OL,14,Freopened.
OL,16,FAnyone with information or relevant
OL,17,Ffootage is asked to contact police on
OL,18,F0161 856 4741, quoting log number 111
OL,19,Fof October 31, 2025.
